.el .ds Aq '
.TH dkp-chunk 1  "chunk 0.1.0" 
.SH NAME
dkp\-chunk \- Retrieve the top\-N most relevant retrieval chunks for a query
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdkp chunk\fR [\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-\-top\fR] [\fB\-\-min\-confidence\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-\-audience\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] <\fIPACK\fR> <\fIQUERY\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Retrieve the top\-N most relevant retrieval chunks for a query
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR [default: plain]
Output format
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
plain: Human\-readable plain text (default)
.IP \(bu 2
table: Aligned table using comfy\-table
.IP \(bu 2
json: Pretty\-printed JSON
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-top\fR \fI<TOP>\fR [default: 5]
Number of chunks to return
.TP
\fB\-\-min\-confidence\fR \fI<F>\fR
Filter by minimum confidence score
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress informational output; print only results
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Print debug info (schema paths, provider calls, etc.)
.TP
\fB\-\-audience\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Filter content to assets tagged for a specific audience profile
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.TP
<\fIPACK\fR>
Path to the DKP bundle directory
.TP
<\fIQUERY\fR>
Query string
.SH VERSION
v0.1.0
